    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it's basically a time capsule! I've taken such good care of it that it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning shape, both inside and out, and drives like a total dream. I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
